  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was the head of it over there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Unloading.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Germans.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I'm sure he, he knew everything, because he was a big, big man.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just Jewish.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Garbage, garbage, what came there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Garbage.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was apart from the ghetto, but was a big place where the train goes in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They, they, they moved everything, download it, till they, they spread this in the stores where they have to supply for the people, the Jewish.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it was a nice size of this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He came home one day, and he said he has trouble with the knee.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my sister says-- my mother was already very sad-- very, very, very like done.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She saw, like, an end to it, you know, the whole thing in '43.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, so she saw an end to it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so she was not that, you know, effective, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my sister says, you know, Melech, come on, let's go to the hospital, some hospital.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they took him to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she left him there, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They just died there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "People [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You never visited him in the hospital?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't even know where this is and was nothing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You're [INAUDIBLE] in like an animal.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I went there, and I said I'm Melech's brother, a Jewish guy, a Jewish guy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not this head.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, it was another two, two people that were lower that-- closer to the people, go do this, do that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The big shot was-- in the beginning I thought he's not Jewish even, this big guy with the boots, you know, high.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember here, nice, nice, Polish military boots with the pants like this, you know, white here.",
